title: Imperial Island 2 The Search for New Land v1.0-ZEKE
description:
Imperial Island 2 The Search for New Land v1.0-ZEKE

Extract 7zip, install with exe & play!

  .: Description :.

  In this latest installment of Imperial Island, accompany Emperor Omadan on an
  exciting journey through uncharted lands in search of his son - Prince Caleb.
  Be careful! The journey by sea is dangerous and the jungles are dense and
  wild. You will need to keep your wits about you to overcome the pirates,
  dragons and sea creatures you encounter along the way. Overcome all obstacles
  to find Prince Caleb in this Match-3 Adventure!

      - 100 exciting levels to master!
      - Timed and relaxed game modes available
      - Earn achievements
      - Brilliant artwork and relaxing soundtrack
      - Try Imperial Island: Birth of an Empire


  .: Installation Notes :.

  1. Run the setup.exe
  2. Have fun !


  .: Greetings :.

  Fly out to DELiGHT, NOY, CRD, RELOADED, RESTORE, SUBSTANCE, TBE
